content.title: About
text: Hi there, and welcome to my page!
I'm Mo, a web Dev constantly trying out new stuff with the goal to improve on every project.
Especially working with 3D web integration, tensorflow and the first steps into the world of web3, I focus on advancing my experience with a hands-on approach.

content.title: Work
text: - Online shop for own brand "Brighter. Clothing"
- Basic gallery app using ionic framework
- Python instagram bot using selenium (inspired by instaPy)
- Webpage creation using CRA for private inquiry
- GLB to USDZ converter using docker. Integrated into django backend
- RnD - Remeshing / UV projection / normal map baking pipeline using pymeshlab / pymesh / blender
- Tesseract OCR for reformatting of scanned image documents into HTML
- Piqups - Webpage using tfjs models to provide pickup lines
